snippet.title: Amber Heard the Acolyte in Star Wars series from Leslye Headland?
snippet.description:
#StarWars #HighRepublic #TheAcolyte

 Rumors are swirling that Amber Heard is being considered for a role in an upcoming Star Wars project from Lucasfilm at Disney.  Is there any merit to these rumors?  

In this video, we will have some fun and explore if there could be any truth to them; as well as assess the baggage Lucasfilm would have to contend with, if they indeed were to cast Amber Heard.
